
                   <p style="text-align: center">
                       <b>Title:</b> Steps
1. Select CONFIGURATION > Network > Load balancer endpoints.
2. Select Create.
3. For the Enter endpoint details step, complete the following fields.<br>
                       <b>Bounding box:</b> x1=184, y1=530, x2=1566, y2=1392
                   </p>
